The '''Moonlight Crystal Lodge''' was a vacation resort on the polar ice caps of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. The resort featured turbo-skiing slopes and private glaciers as well as cold-air heated springs and luxurious restaurants.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

